name: サイトウ - Bea Pokémon
description:
A LoRA of Bea from Pokemon. Trained on NAI.

Works well with a strenght of 1. See samples for good prompts. Doesn't requires a trigger word.

Should work on most of the anime models like Anything v4.5 and AOM3.

Please review this LoRA if you like it or if you encounter a problem!

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
